keepConnect.name: Noho hono
keepConnect.helperText: Mena ka paatohia e koe te hononga tiimata, ka mau tonu te hono. Me whai whakaaro tenei kia rite tonu te hono o te hononga i muri i te hononga.

url.helperText: Hei URL hono, hei tauira WS: //192.168.0.2: 7001, ko WWS ranei: //example.com/path
url.error: Ko te URL tika he URL e tiimata ana me te WS: //, WWS ranei: //
